videos.description: Lamonte Turner drills a 3-pointer from the top of the key, then pulls up in transition to give Tennessee their first lead of the game over Kansas.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCB Highlight (Vols jump ahead on Turner's back-to-back buckets) 2018/11/23 ESHEET

videos.headline: Vols jump ahead on Turner's back-to-back buckets

videos.description: Charlie Moore drives the lane and somehow manages to finish through Jordan Bowden as he gets knocked off balance.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Moore hits circus shot to beat shot clock) 2018/11/23 ESHEET

videos.headline: Moore hits circus shot to beat shot clock

videos.description: Jordan Bone pulls up from deep to beat the first-half buzzer and give Tennessee a 33-31 advantage heading into the break.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Bone hits 3-ball to give Vols halftime lead) 2018/11/23 ESHEET

videos.headline: Bone hits 3-ball to give Vols halftime lead

videos.description: Grant Williams draws a double team and makes a beautiful wrap-around pass to Kyle Alexander, who down the big slam over Dedric Lawson.

tracking.trackingName: NCB One-Play (Alexander throws down one-handed jam over Lawson) 2018/11/23 ESHEET

videos.headline: Alexander throws down one-handed jam over Lawson

videos.description: John Fulkerson finds a cutting Yves Pons, who rises up and finishes between three Jayhawk defenders.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Pons elevates for nasty two-handed stuff) 2018/11/23 ESHEET

videos.headline: Pons elevates for nasty two-handed stuff

videos.description: Lagerald Vick tries to finish in transition, but Kyle Alexander chases him down and swats it off the backboard with emphasis.
videos.headline: Alexander glasses Vick's layup

videos.description: Dedric Lawson hits Udoka Azubuike for a two-handed jam in the paint, then Lagerald Vick pulls up from deep to tie the Vols at 56-56.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCB Highlight (Kansas ties game with Azubuike dunk, Vick triple) 2018/11/23 ESHEET

videos.headline: Kansas ties game with Azubuike dunk, Vick triple

videos.description: Devon Dotson charges down the court and gets a layup on the glass as he's fouled, getting the goaltending call after Admiral Schofield's late block.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Dotson gets goaltending call for and-1 in OT) 2018/11/23 ESHEEET

videos.headline: Dotson gets goaltending call for and-1 in OT

videos.description: Lagerald Vick throws it up for Dedric Lawson, who puts it down with two hands to give the Jayhawks a 78-73 lead in overtime.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Vick lobs to Lawson for clutch alley-oop) 2018/11/23 ESHEET

videos.headline: Vick lobs to Lawson for clutch alley-oop

videos.description: Jordan Bowden turns it over, and Dedric Lawson capitalizes by running the floor and flushing down a one-handed jam to make it 82-75 Jayhawks late in the extra frame.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Lawson extends OT lead with huge fast-break slam) 2018/11/23 ESHEET

videos.headline: Lawson extends OT lead with huge fast-break slam
